column5: Straightening out my dock this morning (07:00 am) after the ice and high waters this past spring moved the whole thing out about 2 feet...  We got her back in place and changed the two front poles for two of the proper size...(no shims needed now...  )  Many thanks to Meeley, Buckster and Crappieperchhunter for a job well done...  Another kudos to the OFC site...
